學習規範 Course Policy
	    This is a one-semester two-credit course. We will introduce the concept of the metabolic diseases and select several critical topics related to organelle stress on the metabolism-related diseases from the top journals. The course will include lecture and presentation/discussion from students. Students will be divided into 8 groups. Each group should introduce the background related to the current topic in organelle stress & metabolic disease, experimental design, key methodology and tools, and finally the assigned article.      

